Package: NormalGamma
Type: Package
Title: Normal-gamma convolution model
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2011-12-20
Author: S. Plancade and Y. Rozenholc
Maintainer: Sandra Plancade <sandra.c.plancade@uit.no>
Description: The functions proposed in this package compute the density of the sum of a gaussian and a gamma random variables, estimate the parameters and correct the noise effect in a gamma-signal and gaussian-noise model. This package has been used to implement the background correction method for Illumina microarray data presented in Plancade S., Rozenholc Y. and Lund E. (http://arxiv.org/abs/1112.4180).
